Package: GLaRe
Type: Package
Title: Graphical Assessment of Latent Feature Representations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Edward", "Gunning",
           email = "edward.gunning@pennmedicine.upenn.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Emma", "Zohner",
           email = "etraore@gmail.com",
           role = "aut"))
Description: Implements methods for assessing the losslessness of latent feature
    representations for complex object-valued data using out-of-sample performance.
    The package provides tools for computing losslessness measures and for visualizing
    results through graphical displays, including an interactive Shiny-based interface.
